author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Dow Biomedica To Distribute Biohit Gastropanel In Korea
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - BIOHIT OYJ:
* DOW BIOMEDICA TO DISTRIBUTE BIOHIT GASTROPANEL® IN KOREA * ‍REGISTRATION WILL START DURING 1(ST) QUARTER OF 2018.​ * ‍BIOHIT OYJ AND DOW BIOMEDICA HAVE SIGNED AN AGREEMENT FOR DISTRIBUTION OF BIOHIT GASTROPANEL IN KOREA​
* ‍CONTRACT HAS BEEN SIGNED FOR FOUR YEARS WITH A CONTINUATION OPTION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
